Hellpeon grabbed his face with one hand as Ultimos beak went into and 
actually through his other, causing him to scream out in pain once 
more. However this also set Ultimo up and Hellpeon intended using 
this posistion to attempt to end the battle now. Quickly he moved his 
hand away from his face and towards Ultimos midsection before 
unleashing a large beam fo Chaochitan energy.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., gunthers@t... wrote:
> Ultimo Campeon tried to hang on with the one claw that had 
> managed to grapple his head but Hellpeons strength pried it off.  
> The large beak of Ultimo reached down to try and bite the hand.
